# ============================================================================
# Notes
# ============================================================================
#
# How to use this file:
#
# 1. Code owners are automatically requested for review when PRs touch their files
# 2. More specific patterns override general ones
# 3. You can specify multiple owners per pattern
# 4. Use @username for individuals, @org/team for teams
# 5. Empty lines and comments (starting with #) are ignored
#
# As the team grows, add new owners in the specific expertise areas section.
# This ensures proper review coverage for specialized components.
#
# For more information:
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
